Class StringMapSchema<V>

All Implemented Interfaces:
Schema<Map<String,V>>
public class StringMapSchema<V>
extends MapSchema<String,V>

A utility schema for a Map with String keys and single-type object values. Keys cannot be null otherwise the entry is ignored (not serialized). Values however can be null.

Author:
David Yu
Date created:
Jun 25, 2010
